Package com.mewna.catnip.entity.guild

Interface Guild

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Entity, Snowflake
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GuildImpl
    public interface Guild
extends Snowflake
    Represents a Discord guild. A guild is colloquially referred to as a server, both in the client UI and by users.
    Since:
    9/6/18
    Author:
    natanbc
